overed Check</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=23447\">checks in q-search</a> by <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Robert Hyatt</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 02, 2008</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Check&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32424\">Standpat and check</a> by <a href=\"/Vlad_Stamate\" title=\"Vlad Stamate\">Vlad Stamate</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 06, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search#StandPat\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Standing Pat</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=51343&amp;sid=2384b91c58dc091e82cef3abd2a4f3f4\">Detecting Checks</a> by beneficii, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Programming Forum</a>, November 27, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=38387\">out of check move ordering</a> by <a href=\"/Don_Dailey\" title=\"Don Dailey\">Don Dailey</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 12, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42971\">checks in quies</a> by <a href=\"/Larry_Kaufman\" title=\"Larry Kaufman\">Larry Kaufman</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 22, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\